data.event: The Municipality of San Antonio is composed of ten barangays (listed here with 2010 population): Burabod - 936 Dalupirit - 1,864 Manraya - 813 Pilar - 683 Rizal - 376 San Nicolas - 517 Vinisitahan - 664 Ward I (Pob.) - 745 Ward II (Pob.) - 759 Ward III (Pob.) - 1,520 The town center (poblacion) is divided into three small barangays: Poblacion Ward I, Poblacion Ward II, and Poblacion Ward III.
